(262, 1, '2016-10-25 10:46:46', '2016-10-25 02:46:46', '<h1>所长</h1>\r\n<div class="person-head">\r\n<a href="/archives/238"><img src="/static/head/teacher/zhoumingquan-2.png" alt="zhoumingquan-2" /></a><div>周明全</div>\r\n</div>\r\n周明全，教授，博士生导师。教育部虚拟现实应用工程研究中心主任，教育部计算机科学与技术委员会软件工程教学指导委员会委员。北京师范大学虚拟现实与可视化技术研究中心主任。中国计算机学会理事，中国中文信息学会理事，中国计算机教育学会常务理事，陕西省计算机学会副理事长。\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n<h1>副所长</h1>\r\n<div class="person-head">\r\n<a href="/archives/240"><img src="/static/head/teacher/wuzhongke-2.jpg" alt="wuzhongke-2" /></a><div>武仲科</div>\r\n</div>\r\n武仲科，北京师范大学信息科学与技术学院教授，博士生导师，教育部高等学校动画、数字媒体专业教学指导委员会委员。主要研究方向：计算机图形学与计算机辅助几何设计、计算机动画，虚拟现实、医学图象处理等。', '研究所领导', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '195-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-25 10:46:46', '2016-10-25 02:46:46', '', 195, 'http://localhost:8000/archives/262', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(294, 1, '2016-10-25 11:30:16', '2016-10-25 03:30:16', '<div class="person-info"><img src="/static/head/teacher/wuzhongke-1.jpg" alt="wuzhongke-1" />\r\n<h1>基本信息</h1>\r\n\r\n职称：教授, 博士生导师\r\n\r\n联系电话：58803055\r\n\r\n邮箱： zwu@bnu.edu.cn\r\n\r\n<h1>社会兼职</h1>\r\n\r\n国际数字考古协会执行委员会委员\r\n\r\n北京图形图像学会常务理事\r\n\r\n<h1>教育经历</h1>\r\n\r\n1984/09-1988/09：理学学士，北京大学数学系基础数学专业\r\n\r\n1988/09-1991/01：硕士，北京航空航天大学航空宇航制造工程专业CAD/CAM方向\r\n\r\n1991/09-1995/09：博士，北京航空航天大学飞机设计系CAD/CAM 方向\r\n\r\n<h1>研究领域</h1>\r\n\r\n计算机图形学、计算机辅助几何设计、计算机动画、虚拟现实、医学图象处理\r\n\r\n<h1>主持项目</h1>\r\n\r\n2012-2015：国家自然科学基金项目，盘B样条和球B样条造型的理论及其应用\r\n\r\n2009-2012：中央高校基本科研业务费专项资金资助，文化遗产保护中大数据集全自动配准和匹配技术。\r\n\r\n<h1>获奖情况</h1>\r\n\r\n2009年国家科学进步二等奖，文物虚拟修复和数字化保护技术的研究与应用，排名第六）\r\n\r\n2008年新加坡南洋理工大学访问教授(Visiting Professor)\r\n\r\n2007年新加坡南洋理工大学Tan Chin Tuan学术交流学者奖\r\n\r\n2006年教育部科技进步二等奖，三维刚体破损复原研究及其在文物虚拟修复中应用，排名第六\r\n\r\n<h1>研究经历</h1>\r\n\r\n2006年4月至今，北京师范大学信息科学与技术学院教授，博士生导师。\r\n\r\n1995年9月至1997年9月，在中国科学院软件研究所从事博士后研究，并于1997年9月，在该所获副研究员职称。\r\n\r\n1997年9月至1999年8月，在新加坡南洋理工大学计算机工程系从事博士后研究。\r\n\r\n从1999年8月到2006年4月，分别在新加坡国家高性能计算研究所(IHPC)，法国国家信息与自动化研究所(INRIA)，新加坡南洋理工大学(NTU)计算机工程系等从事科研工作。主持和参与了多项研究和开发工作，涉及了计算机图形学各个方面。\r\n\r\n<h1>文章专著</h1>\r\n\r\n<strong>国际知名杂志</strong>\r\n\r\nYuYun Tian, Fuqing Duan, Mingquan Zhou, Zhongke Wu. Active contour model combining region and edge information. Machine Vision and Applications.(online).\r\n\r\n1. Qingqiong Deng, Mingquan Zhou, Wuyang Shui, Zhongke Wu, Yuan Ji, Ruyi Bai, A Novel Skull Registration Based on Global and Local Deformations for Craniofacial Reconstruction，Forensic Science International, V208, n1-3, 2011.\r\nZ Nan Hu, Suiping Zhou, Zhongke Wu, Mingquan Zhou, Benjamin Eng Keong Cho: Spatial-temporal patterns and pedestrian simulation. Journal of Visualization and Computer Animation 21(3-4): 387-399 (2010).\r\nZhZhongke Wu, Feng Lin, Seah Hock Soon: Topology preserving voxelisation of rational Bézier and NURBS curves. Computers &amp; Graphics 27(1): 83-89 (2003).\r\n\r\n2. Zhongke WU, Seah Hock Soon, Lin Feng, Tunnel-free Voxelization of Rational Bezier and NURBS Surfaces, The Visual Computer, Volume 19, Numbers 7-8: 505—512, 2003.\r\n\r\n3. Wu Zhongke, Lin Feng, Seah Hock Soon and Chan Kai Yun, Evaluation of difference bounds for computing rational Bézier curves and surfaces. Computers &amp; Graphics 28(4): 551-558 (2004).\r\n\r\n4. Jie Qiu, Hock Soon Seah, Feng Tian, ZhongKe Wu, Quan Chen. Feature and Region Based Auto Painting for 2D Animation，The Visual Computer, v21, n11:928-944, 2005.\r\n\r\n5. Jie Qiu, Hock Soon Seah, Feng Tian, Quan Chen, ZhongKe Wu. Enhanced Auto Coloring with Hierarchical Region Matching. Journal of Computer Animation and Virtual World. 16(3-4):463-473, 2005.\r\n\r\n6. Quan Chen, Feng Tian, HockSoon Seah, Zhongke Wu, Jie Qiu, Melikhov Konstantin. DBSC-based animation enhanced with feature and motion. Computer Animation and Virtual Worlds, Volume 17, Issue 3-4 (July 2006), p 189-198.\r\n\r\n7. Jie Qiu, Hock Soon Seah, Feng Tian, Quan Chen, Zhongke Wu and Konstantin Melikhov. Auto Coloring with Character Registration. International Journal of Computer Games Technology. V2008\r\n\r\n8. LIN Feng¬, SEAH Hock Soon, WU Zhongke, MA Di. Voxelisation and Fabrication of Freeform Models. Virtual and Physical Prototyping, Vol 2 n2, 2007: 65–73\r\n\r\n<strong>国际会议</strong>\r\n\r\nJianping Cai, Zhongke Wu, Xingce Wang, Mingquan Zhou. Adaptive Moving Least Squares for Smoothing Point Clouds. The Twelfth IASTED International Conference on Computer Graphics and Imaging (CGIM 2011)\r\nChang Leng, Zhongke Wu, Mingquan Zhou, Reconstruction of Tubular Object with Ball B-Spline Curve, Computer Graphics International (CGI) 2011.\r\n\r\n1. Zhongke Wu, Hock Soon Seah, Mingquan Zhou. Skeleton based Parametric Solid Models: Ball B-Spline Curves. Proceedings of 10th IEEE International Conference on Computer-Aided Design and Computer Graphics. Beijing, 2007. 47-52\r\n\r\n2. Zhongke Wu, Hock Soon Seah, Mingquan Zhou. Skeleton based Parametric Solid Models: Ball B-Spline Surfaces. Proceedings of 10th IEEE International Conference on Computer-Aided Design and Computer Graphics. Beijing, 2007. 421-424\r\n\r\n3. Hock Soon Seah, Zhongke Wu, Feng Tian, Xuexiang Xie, Yixiang Lu, Xian Xiao. MODELING AND VISUALIZATION OF PLANTS WITH BALL B-SPLINES. The International Workshop on Advanced Image Technology (IWAIT) 2007, Bangkok, Thailand. January 8-9, 2007.\r\n\r\n4. Zhongke Wu, Mingquan Zhou, Xingce Wang, Xuefeng Ao and Rongqing Song. An Interactive System of Modeling 3D Trees with Ball B-Spline Curves. The Second International Symposium on Plant Growth Modeling, Simulation, Visualization and Applications (PMA06). Beijing (PR CHINA), November 13-17, 2006\r\n\r\n5. Hock Soon Seah, Zhongke Wu, Feng Tian, Xian Xiao, Xie Boya. Artistic Brushstroke Representation and Animation with Disk B-Spline Curve. ACM SIGCHI International Conference on Advances in Computer Entertainment Technology (ACE 2005), 15th - 17th June 2005. Polytechnic University of Valencia (UPV), Spain (Full paper))\r\n\r\n6. Seah Hock Soon, Wu Zhongke. Ball B-Spline based Geometric Models in Distributed Virtual Environments. Workshop towards Semantic Virtual Environments\' (SVE 2005), Villars, Switzerland.\r\n\r\n8. Quan Chen, Zhongke WU, Feng Tian, Hock Soon Seah, Jie Qiu, Melikhov Konstantin. Vectorization of Raster Line-Drawings in Cartoons, International Conference on Computer Animation and Social Agents, October 17 - 19, 2005, Hong Kong\r\n\r\n9. XueXiang Xie, Feng Tian, HockSoon Seah, Zhongke Wu, Konstantin Melikhov. Pencil Drawing for NPR Rendering and Animation. Computer Animation &amp; Social Agents 2006(CASA’06)\r\n\r\n10. J. Qiu, H.S. Seah, F. Tian, Z. Wu, and Q. Chen. Topology enhanced feature-based auto coloring for computer-assisted cel animation. The Seventh IASTED International Conference on Computer Graphics and Imaging, 2004, p 26-32, Kauai, Hawaii, USA August 17-19, 2004.\r\n\r\n13. Hock Soon Seah, Zhongke Wu, Feng Tian, Xian Xiao, Xie Boya. Interactive Free-hand Drawing and In-Between Generation with DBSC. ACM SIGCHI International Conference on Advances in Computer Entertainment Technology (ACE 2005), 15th - 17th June 2005. Polytechnic University of Valencia (UPV), Spain (Demo)\r\n\r\n14. Xie Xuexiang, Tian Feng, Seah Hock Soon, Wu Zhongke. Texture space stylization for NPR rendering and animation. International Conference Computer Graphics, Imaging and Vision （CGIV05）, 26 – 29 July 2005，Beijing, China\r\n\r\n</div>', '武仲科', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '240-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-25 11:30:16', '2016-10-25 03:30:16', '', 240, 'http://localhost:8000/archives/294', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
